--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SUPPORTED PLATFORMS

    Tested: Linux, Windows 7, OSX, Android {4.4, 5.0}, BlackBerry 10, iOS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PREBUILT PACKAGES

    Windows  : https://github.com/iamsergio/flow-pomodoro/releases
    Android  : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kdab.flow_pomodoro
    Archlinux: https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/flow-pomodoro/
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DEPENDENCIES

  Qt >= 5.3.0 (QtDeclarative, QtQuickControls and QtGraphicalEffects)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
BUILD

    qmake && make
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INSTALL

    make INSTALL_ROOT=/usr/local/ install
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
